==English==

===Adverbial phrase===
'''just now'''
#(Standard English) At present. Now at the moment.
#*"We do not have that item in stock '''just now'''."
#(South African) In a little while. Shortly, which could mean within ten minutes or two hours or at same indeterminate time within the near future.
#*"I'll be coming '''just now'''. 
#(South African) In the immediate past.
#* I was talking to my friend on the phone '''just now'''.
